<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr> Burst Agro and Shroud of Stealth Fixes Incoming<br>
There was a problem introduced with the patch on 4-8-03 that caused unusual amounts of agro to be created by those doing large amounts of damage in a very short time (including things like crits, Manaburn and Trueshot). We are aware of the problem and we're working on a fix for that right now. We hope to patch to repair the issue some time in the next 24 hours. <br>
<br>
There has been an increase in the number of NPCs that can see through Shroud of Stealth. We are aware of this issue and are working on a fix for it. I can't say for certain when it will be fixed, but we are aware of it. <br>
<br>
Thank you for your patience while we correct these issues. <br>
<br>
Alan  <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
/em breathes a sigh of relief.<br>
<br>
They did indeed change this.  I was in inner camp in PoV last night for 2 hours and only got aggro once, and I deserved it <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Glad to hear they took a quick look at it.  Thanks SOE (how often do you hear THAT ????)<br>
<br>
Baron Garrath Moore<br>
