I certainly hope this is not an omen.  Crits have never caused <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>any</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> aggro at all.  If all they are going to do is turn down the amount of aggro that is being generated by crits, then I see this last patch as a clever marketing ploy: Implement something very heinous that makes everyone complain.  After the complaints come in, tone it down somewhat, but leave it worse than it was before the initial patch.  Nobody complains because it seems like they just did something good, when in fact the nerf is still present when compared to conditions before the first patch.<br>
<br>
Can we get someone to please test crits and let us know if they are generating any aggro at all now?<br>
<br>
Thanks,<br>
<br>
-Raystonn<br>
