<br>
The interesting question is did this patch roll back the agro rewrite or it is still generating hate based on DPS, but either ignoring crits/focus effects, or just using the damage of the nuke to calculate DPS. (rather than damage done)<br>
<br>
From what I've seen so far agro is definately more 'normal', xp group in BoT was fine, no agro at all, and I did 35k to Doomshade w/o any agro, including 3 4800+ crits in a row.  But it is still not clear if hate is working off DPS or damage.<br>
